author: @lilox87
text: Today is your birthday, what should I start with? What are the letters that suit you? What letters describe your beauty, your splendor, and the brilliance of the day you were born? How do I begin, and you are the beginning, and touch is the end. I wish you knew how your light fell upon my nights. You are as distinct as a mother’s invitation from a family member’s invitation, like the line under which we put a line, like a Georgian rose in a barren desert. I wish you knew how you were. I had a compass when I lost my way. I wish you knew what you were to me? You are my star among billions of stars and asteroids. I chose you to become a gemini in my lonely paths. You are the beginning of the road and its happy end. Every year, your heart is touched only by all goodness and all knowledge. Happiness is a twin to your soul that does not leave you, and every year your mouth spreads smiles. I wish you a year as prosperous as your beating heart with beauty. On your birthday, I am far from you, but I live in your heart. It is true for whom I can clap and celebrate with you closely, but I will look at the star and tell him what I wish for you and it will reach you, Jimin. You are my bright star that collapsed my darkness. You are everything to me. I love you, my dearest celebrity and the closest to my heart. Every year, you are a piece of me. The sky is cloudy and no one is like it. Every year, you are something that does not happen twice. Jimin. Every year, you are a laugh that takes me to what they do not know. Every year, I am with you. Every year, you are my happiness, the soul of my soul, and its life. Every year, your heart is full of roses and love. Every year, your laugh never disappears. Every year, you are loved. And I love you every year, my sweetest and most precious soul. I love and value you every year, and I see you as a light on this earth. Every year, you are well. Every year, butterflies fly around you to lead you to a path and always progress. Every year, I see your beauty. 🎀💕
